snippet.title: Hardcore Cottagecore - Announcement Trailer - Steam
snippet.description:
Mushroom meadow is being devastated by hundreds of drones who want to build another Amazon warehouse! It’s time for these fungi to fight back with wild auto-firing cottagecore abilities! Choose your mushroom, go it solo or team up with your best bud, survive the horde and win back your turf! 

Wishlist "Hardcore Cottagecore" on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2753330/Hardcore_Cottagecore/
